the show - the 45th anniversary celebration of children''s hockey school,я Kirov-Chepetsk', 'This Full multifunctional sports facility with the area of 12730 m2. Construction has two-storeys and a ground floor.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt Ground floor - block of entertainment and sportsпfacilities : bodyfitness gym, billiards room, sauna, fitness center, four large comfortable changing rooms with showers and bathrooms, separate cloakroom for coaches.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt First floor - a big gym, bodybuilding gym (for the gym there are special locker rooms with special showers, toilets), a block of luxury changing rooms for athletes with dryers, workshops for sharpening of skates, shower rooms, bathrooms with separate locker rooms for coaches, buffet bar for 600 meals for staff and trainers, turbosolarium, a press center, rental store.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt Second floor. Big lobby of the second floor allows viewers to bypass the ice arena in a circle. The lobby has wardrobes, shops, fast food units. On the second floor there is a cafe with 60 seats. Ice arena may take in the mode of sports competitions - 2,000 people in the concert mode more than 3,000 spectators.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt Ice Palace &quot Olympus - Arena&quot  located in the park area of the city. The land area 41726 m2. Around the palace there are lawns on different levels, flowerbeds park with children''s playground, parking for 200 cars, vip parking and emergency vehicles. Asphalt paths with length of 1200 m. are used forп roller skating which can also be rented . Hire of the palace can provide 200 pairs of ski skates of different sizes for both hockey and figure-skating. Ice Palace &quot Olympus - Arena&quot  has the ability to organize and conduct competitions in all sports games, table tennis, tennis, wrestling, boxing, rhythmic and artistic gymnastics, etc.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt At the same time &quot Olympus - Arena&quot  can provide changing rooms for 10 teams. In the palace there is a live concert equipment technology, including lighting equipment, sound, special effects equipment, equipment for the laser show, collapsible stage that will satisfy any technical rider and allow to holdп concerts, entertainment shows at any level.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt During the design and construction of the Ice Palace &quot Olympus - Arena&quot  insulating cushion under the old system was kept with quenched stove ice box, which reduced the price of the cooling system.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt The main volume of the building of the palace is covered multistoried structural slab which has a parachute shape . Parachute shape reduces the forces in the bars and use them for standardized elements structural plates issued by the Moscow plant &quot Mechanization&quot  TU 400-28-101-75 &quot Rods and nodal elements of spatial structures overlap.&quot ', 'Кирово-Чепецкий район', 'Кировская область', NULL, 'г. Кирово-Чепецк', 'Kirovo-Chepetsk', 'Кировская область, г. Кирово-Чепецк, ул. Заводская, 20', '20 Zavodskaya str., Kirov-Chepetsk, Kirov region', 33707000, 'Развитие ФК и спорта в РФ (2006-2015)', 'реконструкция', '1993-01-11', '2010-11-15', 477345000, '09:00-18:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'olimp-arena@yandex.ru', 'арена ледовая', '8 (83361) 4-53-61', 'http://olimp-arena.ru  www.dymka-sport.ru ', 'баскетбол, бодибилдинг, волейбол, кёрлинг, конькобежный спорт, настольный теннис, общая физическая подготовка, спортивная аэробика, теннис, фигурное катание, фитнес-аэробика, футбол, хоккей, хоккей с мячом', 50.0126, 58.5514, 24);
