ая установка оснащается камерой деоазации для нейтрализции не прореагировавшего озона. Для поддержания требуемой температуры в процессе эксплуатацииустановлены 2 водоводяных теплообменника «Bowman» мощностью по 730 кВт. 4. Управление процессами фильтрации, поддержания заданной температуры воды в бассейне, дозирования коагулянта, заданных уровней pH и обеззараживающих веществ, предусматривается в автоматическом режиме.', 'Provides citizens of the Republic of Mari El with opportunity to engage in physical culture and sports, &lt br&gt Contributes to a sustainableяinterest among the population in regular physical training and sports, healthy lifestyle, &lt br&gt Contributes to the creation of an effective system of training of sports reserve and conditions for the development of high performance sport,', '1. Facade architecture - modern construction and finishing materials – sandwich panels, suspended ventilated facades &quot DEKOT XXI&quot  and &quot TALDOM - SPIDI&quot  made of gas and silicate building blocks.The floors are made of the SportsFlooringcep.Taratlex surface.2. Air processing in the supply air systems provides filtration, air heating and sound proofing, automatic temperature control, and filters dust control. 3. To ensure the required quality of water, the continuous automated quality control of HTH Сontrolles plants is provided. A water ozone conditioning plant PROZONEPZ2-24 is additionally installed. The ozonation plant is equipped with an outgassing chamber to neutralize unreacted ozone. To maintain the required temperature during operation, two water-to-water heat exchangers &quot Bowman&quot  with capacity of 730 kW are installed.4. Filtering processes, maintenance of the set temperature of the pool water, coagulant dosage, and set pH and decontaminant levels are automatically controlled. ', 'Город Йошкар-Ола', 'Республика Марий Эл', NULL, 'г. Йошкар-Ола', 'Yoshkar-Ola', 'Республика Марий Эл, г. Йошкар-Ола, ул. Карла-Маркса, 107/а', '107 а Karl Marx