- Выполнение системы отопления залов за счет вентиляции и поддержания температуры в не игровое время только за счет отопления до &#43  5&#186 С также привело к существенной экономии средств при эксплуатации здания. - Выполнение современной системы вентиляции позволило создать комфортные условия для спортсменов и посетителей. -Выполнение дополнительных эвакуационных выходов, разделение потоков спортсменов и посетителей повысило безопасность эксплуатации объекта.  ', 'This facility is of great importance for the city of Novosibirsk, since it is the only specialized sports complex, where you can play games of the Russian championship in volleyball. Games of professional teams help to promote fitness and sports of all segments of the population, for beginners Sports Complex is the place to reach new heights of sports, it promotes good health, a healthy lifestyle in the community.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt The sports complex holds:&lt br&gt - 350 students of Sports School Centre &quot Center for team sports&quot  are engaged in volleyball&lt br&gt - 60 students in boxing,&lt br&gt - 85 students of Sports School &quot Siberia in football&quot ,&lt br&gt The sports complex holds games and training sessions of team in Novosibirsk: &quot Lokomotiv Novosibirsk&quot  (volleyball, Super League),я Dynamo basketball club -the Department of Internal Affairs (basketball - Premier League),я &quot Novosibirsk&quot  (basketball - Super League) - games are visited by a large number of spectators.', 'Total area -10926,8 sq. m. The Great volleyball and basketball courts and a tribune at 2285 seats, volleyball and tennis courtl, medium hall for volleyball, basketball and mini football, volleyball small hall, boxing, karate, table tennis and a gym.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt - Implementation of facade insulation, replacement of windows and stained glass for new, corresponding to modern requirements of of heat engineering protecting buildings will significantly reduce heat loss and heating costs of the sports complex.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt - Implementation of the heating system through the halls of ventilation and keep the temperature at game time not only by heating to + 5 и C also resulted in substantial savings in the operation of the building.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt - Implementation of a modern ventilation system has created favorable conditions for the athletes and visitors.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt -Implementation of additional emergency exits, parallelization of athletes and visitors increased the safety of operation of the building.', 'Город Новосибирск', 'Новосибирская область', NULL, 'г. Новосибирск', 'Novosibirsk', 'Новосибирская область, г. Новосибирск, ул. Учительская, 61', 'Novosibirsk region, Novosibirsk, street Teacher, 61', 50701000, 'Развитие ФК и спорта в РФ (2006-2015)', 'строительство', '2006-06-01', '2011-12-30', 167406200, '08.00 - 20.00', '08.00 - 20.00', '08.00 - 20.00', '10926', 'civs.nsk@mail.ru', 'многофункциональный спортивный комплекс', '8-383-271-02-06', NULL, 'баскетбол, бокс, волейбол, вольная борьба, каратэ, настольный теннис, спортивная гимнастика, танцевальный спорт, футбол', 82.9526, 55.0898, 82);
