ir free time or work, improve the level of physical development, commitment to sport lifestyle, identify talented athletes.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt 1. Created in order to ensure the conditions for practicing the various segments of the population of the municipality &quot City of Ekaterinburg&quot  in physical culture and sports,&lt br&gt 2. The implementation of the full set of reference for municipal founder football Sports School &quot  VIZ &quot ofя Verh-Isetsky area,&lt br&gt 3. The provision of optimal conditions for the organization of meaningful leisure-based free time for the population in physical culture and sports,&lt br&gt 4. The provision of conditions for the organization and conduct of sporting events and organization of sports and fitness events, activities of the municipality &quot City of Ekaterinburg&quot ,&lt br&gt 5. The expansion of the range of public services in the sphere of physical culture and sports.', 'The building houses a multi-purpose gym which size is 24 x 42 m and a 3-storey block serving administrative and residential premises.', 'Город Екатеринбург', 'Свердловская область', NULL, 'г. Екатеринбург', 'Yekaterinburg', 'Свердловская область, г. Екатеринбург, ул. Опалихинская, 23/а ', '620034, Sverdlovsk region, Ekaterinburg, street Opalihinskaya 23a ', 65701000, 'Развитие ФК и спорта в РФ (2006-2015)', 'строительство', '2008-01-07', '2009-12-24', 116383000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'fokvi@mail.ru', 'многофункциональный спортивный комплекс', '8-912-622-39-33, ', NULL, 'бадминтон, гандбол, мини-футбол, настольный теннис, стритбол', 60.5628, 56.8527, 2);
