ются: •    применение энергосберегающих технологий &#40 теплоизоляционный материал&#41  •    собственная котельная на газообразном топливе •    современное синтетическое покрытие пола спортивного зала ', 'In connection with the commissioning in November 2012 of low cost og sports gym in the village Tazinskaya there was a rise of interest in the village Tazinskaya to the sphere of physical culture and sports. Sports clubs to practice with children, youth and adults were organized.&lt br&gt This had a positive impact on the overall performance of students'' health. The number of children to primary athletic group has grown.&lt br&gt &lt br&gt During the autumn-springяon the basis of sports gym, a large number of sports events are held including:&lt br&gt &lt br&gt ? Zonal district basketball games&lt br&gt The final regional competitions in basketball&lt br&gt ? championship on different kinds of sports among settlements of Tatsinskiy area (among adults)&lt br&gt ? Cups on different kinds of sports among settlements of Tatsinskiy area (among adults)&lt br&gt ? Zonal district competitions in mini -football&lt br&gt The final regional competitions in mini -football&lt br&gt ? championship among educational institutions of Tatsinskiy area (in children)&lt br&gt ? open areas, regional tournaments on different kinds of sports (including children)&lt br&gt &lt br&gt ? match meetings&lt br&gt ? villageя competitions&lt br&gt On the basis of low-cost sports gym in the village Tazinskaya, Tatsinskaya school ь 1conducts lessons on physical training, Youth Sports School holds training sessions on football, basketball, boxing .', 'The main significant technological solutions are:&lt br&gt &lt br&gt ? use of energy-saving technologies (insulation material)&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt ? boiler house on gaseous fuels&lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt &lt br&gt ? Modern synthetic flooring sports gym', 'Тацинский район', 'Ростовская область', NULL, 'ст. Тацинская', 'Tazinskaya village', 'Ростовская область, ст. Тацинская, ул. Октябрьская, 61 ', 'Rostov region, stanitsaTatsinskaya, st. October, 61 ', 60654465, 'Развитие ФК и спорта в РФ (2006-2015)', 'строительство', NULL, '2012-12-18', 16216600, '11:00-20:30', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'mboy.school1@yandex.ru', 'зал спортивный', '8(86397) 3-03-94', NULL, 'армспорт (армрестлинг), бадминтон, баскетбол, бокс, волейбол, гиревой спорт, дартс, каратэ, настольный теннис, фитнес-аэробика, футбол, черлидинг', 41.2807, 48.1885, 2);
