временная система водоочистки, покрытие сооружения энергосберегающими материалами, установлен теплоутилизатор и частотные регуляторы в системе вентиляции- кондиционирования с  программированием их работы,  расходомеры на холодной и горячей воде в душевых помещениях  ', 'Social objects: creating conditions for strengthening the public health of the Altai Territory through the development of sports infrastructure, promotion of mass and professional sports (including elite sport) and the attracion of various segments of the population to regular physical training and sports.&lt br&gt Dates of major events and significant events:&lt br&gt Championship of the Altai Krai in Basketball among girls born in 1996 -1997.&lt br&gt 23-26.02.2013&lt br&gt - Regional Basketball Tournament in memory of N.F. Chernukhina among veterans and young men born in 2001-2002 27-03.2013&lt br&gt - VI Summer Games of students of Altai Krai in basketball among boys 14-17.03.2013&lt br&gt Championship of the Altai Krai in volleyball among girls born in 1999-2000&lt br&gt 04-07.04.2013&lt br&gt Championship of the Altai Krai in basketball among girls born in 1996-1996&lt br&gt 17-21.04.2013&lt br&gt Open 15 &quot International Tournament&quot  Siberia Asia ?Open Championship of the Altai Territory (kumite, kata) 28-30 .09. 2013&lt br&gt The first phase of the Children''s Festival of Altai Krai in volleyball among girls born in 2001-2003 &quot Here the stars are lit&quot  02-03.11.2013&lt br&gt Championship of the Altai Krai in basketball among boys born in 1998&lt br&gt 01-05.05.14&lt br&gt Open Championship &quot Jubilee &quot in swimming devoted to&quot  Children''s Day &quot with the participation of the strongest teams in the Altai Krai and Kemerovo region.&lt br&gt 30.05-01.06.2014&lt br&gt - Regional Badminton Tournament in memory ofя G.S. Titov. 25-27.04.2014', 'Modern water treatment system, covering the construction with energy-saving materials, installed heat exchanger and frequency regulators in the ventilation system - air conditioning with programming their work, flowmeters at the cold and hot water in the shower rooms', 'Рубцовский район', 'Алтайский край', NULL, 'г. Рубцовск', 'Rubtsovsk', 'Алтайский край, г. Рубцовск, пр-т Ленина, 203 ', '658225, Altai region, Rubtsovsk city, Lenina 203. ', 1716000, 'Развитие ФК и спорта в РФ (2006-2015)', 'строительство', NULL, '2007-09-03', 149488021, '08:00-22:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'yubilejniy@yandex.ru', 'многофункциональный спортивный комплекс', '8-38557-9-15-50 8-905-082-29-64 ', NULL, 'аквааэробика, бадминтон, баскетбол, волейбол, каратэ, киокусинкай, плавание, теннис, фитнес-аэробика, черлидинг', 81.2066, 51.4911, 2);
