ll that helps to develop their need for a healthy lifestyle.&lt br&gt Dates of major events and significant events:&lt br&gt 2012, 2013, 2014 regional football tournament for the prize of the club &quot Leather Ball&quot ,&lt br&gt 2012, 2013. 2014 - Championship of Yagodninsky District Cup.&lt br&gt (also _ the stadium holdsя football competitions on the Day of Youth, Children''s Day, the Day of the village, cross-country race, etc.).', 'Construction was carried out using standard technologies', 'Ягоднинский район', 'Магаданская область', NULL, 'пос. Ягодное', 'village Yagodnoe', 'Магаданская область, пос. Ягодное, ул. Металлистов, 2', 'Magadan region, the village of Berry Street Metallistov 2', 44722000, 'Развитие ФК и спорта в РФ (2006-2015)', 'реконструкция', '2010-06-22', '2011-06-06', 20230045, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sportkom16@rambler.ru', 'футбольное поле ', '(841343)23110', NULL, 'футбол', 149.6213, 62.5241, 2);
